{"tid":1463663,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"嗌stand with hk fight for freedom嗌到悶","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:31:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:49:08.000Z","uid":99876,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3525fc908778e81fce58983deda353e9119ec280","tid":1463663,"uid":99876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:31:40.000Z","msg":"我知叫口號呢樣野唔應該理佢悶唔悶<br />\n呢個口號 無疑有用<br />\n但宣染到嘅情緒較少 又少d實質內容<br />\n手足可能會悶叫少左<br />\n<br />\n加上前日發生嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得可以叫<br />\n1. an eye (for an eye)<br />\n2. 以眼還眼 or 黑警還眼<br />\n3. 不分藍黃 (只分黑白) <br />\n4. no rioters (but tyranny) <br />\n等等啦<br />\n<br />\n雖然好微小嘅事 但我相信有影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf67f5e8bee5bcdfcae312dda1bf418b71f3f7c","tid":1463663,"uid":86277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:37:26.000Z","msg":"機場嘅話外國人多<br />\n可以請佢地做啲具體啲嘅嘢幫我地<br />\n<br />\n推咗上國際頭版，跟住呢？【國際五大請求】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463264\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463264</a>"},{"pid":"61397e6339c6e7d2eb19267bf355cff087e3f965","tid":1463663,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:50:36.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"11b60fffbffca2689d2b0f1b2170fdf7c1853f1b","tid":1463663,"uid":165102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:56:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55be5fc15912db7d87fbaca1f73d57c62f700146","tid":1463663,"uid":99876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:36:34.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"30e34c87799c591153104f2c2bf61374482d345f","tid":1463663,"uid":136663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:39:48.000Z","msg":"[機場][英文口號]鬼佬唔知你哋嗌乜 Hong Kong Bad Cops! Stop the headshots!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1461544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1461544</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討